Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.76,0:00:14.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome back, Lady Satsuki.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.47,0:00:18.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You did well in the Tri-City\NSchools Raid Trip.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.10,0:00:19.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.73,0:00:23.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,How did it go with\Nthe Director?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.69,0:00:26.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,She was pleased\Nat our results.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.56,0:00:29.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,She has also decided to pay\Na visit to Honnouji Academy.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.78,0:00:31.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Then—
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.53,0:00:33.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. It is time at last.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.39,0:00:36.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be counting on you four.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.47,0:00:40.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Students of Honnouji Academy!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.16,0:00:44.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You did well in the Tri-City\NSchools Raid Trip!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.17,0:00:48.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We eradicated the dens of the Kansai\Nforces and anti-clothing guerillas
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.92,0:00:50.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,and completed our mission.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.46,0:00:56.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,For that reason, we will welcome Honnouji\NAcademy Director Ragyo Kiryuin,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.51,0:00:59.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,and in the Ragyo Stadium\Nthat bears her name,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.85,0:01:02.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,we will hold a grand ceremony!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.14,0:01:07.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome the Director by putting \Nforth all the energies that
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.64,0:01:09.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,you have stored up within you!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.52,0:01:13.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,This is the Honnouji Academy Cultural\N& Sports Grand Festival!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.01,0:01:16.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,CULTURAL & SPORTS GRAND FESTIVAL
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.01,0:01:19.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,EPISODE 17\NTELL ME WHY
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.92,0:02:54.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That's funny.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.88,0:02:58.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I was just thinking that\NI'd have to settle things with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.18,0:03:02.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Right now, you don't have\Nyour Kamui or your scissor.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.43,0:03:08.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Do you honestly think a mere half-naked\Nhigh-schooler can beat me?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.18,0:03:10.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You think your threats\Nare gonna faze me?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.98,0:03:13.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be happy to go\Nfull-on naked for you, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.02,0:03:15.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,No, you can't!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.74,0:03:18.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,A girl only reveals herself \Nin her full glory
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.72,0:03:21.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,to the person the loves \Nmost in the whole world!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.03,0:03:25.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Can you honestly say that you love\NMr. Mohawk that deeply, Ryuko?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.83,0:03:27.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, that's not the point.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.83,0:03:31.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,After all, the reason you wear Senketsu\Nis because you love him best, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.81,0:03:33.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If you didn't, you'd never be able to wear
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.77,0:03:35.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,\Na piece of living clothing cause it'd be icky!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.42,0:03:40.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That's what it means for a maiden to\Nentrust her bare skin to someone!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.26,0:03:45.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ryuko, I am flattered that\Nyou are angry on my behalf.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.39,0:03:48.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But if I may be so bold,\Nput me on.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.98,0:03:51.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Senketsu...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.15,0:03:54.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If you don't,\Nyou'll catch cold.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.56,0:03:55.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That's what you're\Nworried about?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.27,0:03:59.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I can't believe you two...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.04,0:04:01.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Playing at being friends \Nwith clothing again, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.24,0:04:04.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I don't feel like\Nshooting them anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.50,0:04:10.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,This is Osaka?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.68,0:04:12.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,\NThis is horrible...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.09,0:04:13.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I suppose it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.40,0:04:15.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is all the result\Nof the power of Life Fibers.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.98,0:04:18.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,As well as yours and mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.05,0:04:21.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.05,0:04:24.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Mikisugi was right to keep us\Nin the dark up until now.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.64,0:04:28.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Even looking at this, it \Nbeggars belief to be told
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.26,0:04:30.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,\Nthat Life Fibers are lifeforms from outer space.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.35,0:04:33.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,This, coming from you?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.81,0:04:38.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm probably scared.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.44,0:04:43.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's like, something\Nthat was just a brawl
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.49,0:04:46.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,turned into some grand battle full\Nof crazy crap I don't understand
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.45,0:04:50.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,like the fate of humanity and\Nthe extinction of the species or whatever.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.71,0:04:55.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,"I don't give a crap about that!"\NThat's what I really wanted to say.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.54,0:04:59.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But I put the blame on you\Nfor me getting mad.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.67,0:05:03.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,No, you really did get angry\Non my behalf, Ryuko.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.72,0:05:06.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That's the kind\Nof person you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.77,0:05:14.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What's his deal?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.56,0:05:20.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Tsumugu Kinagase's older sister\Ndied in a Life Fiber experiment.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.61,0:05:25.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,After Dr. Matoi founded\NNudist Beach,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.32,0:05:29.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,his top assistant was\NTsumugu's sister, Kinue Kinagase.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.62,0:05:33.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Only Life Fibers\Ncan fight Life Fibers.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.39,0:05:37.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,To create Life Fibers that\Nwould obey a human's will.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.50,0:05:40.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That's what Dr. Matoi and Kinue's\Nresearch was directed towards.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.92,0:05:42.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And during one experiment...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.22,0:05:46.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So she's the "foolish woman"\Nhe mentioned, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.76,0:05:51.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Earlier, he said that\NI'd share her fate.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.43,0:05:53.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, right.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.68,0:05:58.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,"Please continue the experiments."\NThose were Kinue's dying words.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.81,0:06:03.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Dr. Matoi made further improvements\Nand completed Kamui Senketsu.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.11,0:06:06.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Senketsu's Life Fibers have been
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.53,0:06:10.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,spliced with your central \Nnervous system's DNA.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.66,0:06:11.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.79,0:06:15.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That's why he can only\Ncommunicate with and be worn by you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.21,0:06:19.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,He's a combat uniform that\NDr. Matoi made especially for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.50,0:06:22.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Why would Dad\Ndo something like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.59,0:06:25.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,He said he did it\Nto protect you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.93,0:06:31.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell, man?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.93,0:06:35.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Your tea.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.73,0:06:36.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.77,0:06:43.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I've drunk a lot of your tea,\Nhaven't I, Soroi?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.32,0:06:46.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, I have been making it for you\Nsince you were five.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.24,0:06:47.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.36,0:06:49.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ever since that day.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.24,0:06:53.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The day father showed me\NJunketsu for the first time.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.16,0:06:58.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That day, Father said to me...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.89,0:07:03.15,OS,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,"This will be your wedding dress."
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.96,0:07:02.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,"This will be your wedding dress."
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.46,0:07:05.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, I have heard.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.21,0:07:09.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I suppose it was on that day\Nthat all this really began.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.84,0:07:11.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It seems like only yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.43,0:07:15.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Even this tea that I once \Nfound so bitter is now
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.33,0:07:18.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,\Nthe most delicious thing in the world to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.52,0:07:22.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.23,0:07:24.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You... found it bitter?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.57,0:07:26.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I never mentioned that?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.90,0:07:30.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,From the very first cup, you smiled,\Nsaying that it was delicious.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.99,0:07:34.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,To think you were merely humoring me\Nand enduring the bitterness.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.49,0:07:36.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I beg your forgiveness.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.33,0:07:38.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's fine already...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.73,0:07:44.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I suppose I was a\Nkindhearted girl back then.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.00,0:07:49.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Form up! At attention!\NListen closely!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.34,0:07:53.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Tomorrow, the Cultural \N& Sports Grand Festival
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.06,0:07:55.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,\Nwill be held at Honnouji Academy!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.56,0:08:00.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,All No-Star students and \Ntheir parents are to welcome
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.20,0:08:02.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,\NDirector Kiryuin from the spectator seats!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.76,0:08:06.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ceremonial dress uniforms\Nwill be distributed to all of you!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.94,0:08:13.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Gather at the stadium entrance\Nin these uniforms by 8:30 AM!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.82,0:08:17.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Tardiness will not be tolerated!\NUnkempt dress will not be tolerated!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.11,0:08:19.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Assume that even the slightest breach of
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.04,0:08:20.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,\Netiquette will carry the death penalty!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.87,0:08:21.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Dismissed!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.04,0:08:23.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Wait just one minute!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.50,0:08:27.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And who are you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.13,0:08:33.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Barazo Mankanshoku, father of Second\NYear Class K's Mako Mankanshoku!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.34,0:08:34.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,His wife, Sukuyo!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.14,0:08:36.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Their firstborn son, Mataro!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.56,0:08:42.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What a well-mannered family.\NEven the dog introduces itself.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.60,0:08:44.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What do you want?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.44,0:08:45.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Where is Mako?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.11,0:08:50.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I heard that Mako was conscripted\Ninto the Schools Raid Trip.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.44,0:08:54.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The other students have returned,\Nbut not Mako and Ryuko.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.66,0:08:56.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Would you care to\Nexplain that?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.70,0:09:00.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Matoi and Mankanshoku?\NThey are rebels.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.08,0:09:05.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,As the family of rebels, your home\Nis to confiscated
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.50,0:09:07.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,and you are to be banished\Nfrom Honnou Town!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.25,0:09:12.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,However, tomorrow is the\NCultural & Sports Grand Festival.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.19,0:09:12.07,On Top,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,CULTURAL & SPORTS GRAND FESTIVAL
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.07,0:09:13.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I will grant you\Na special pardon!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.07,0:09:18.49,On Top,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,CULTURAL & SPORTS GRAND FESTIVAL\NSPECIAL PARDON
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.47,0:09:16.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You will be allowed\Nto participate!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.76,0:09:20.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If you wish to atone for your daughter's\Ncrimes, participate in the ceremony
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.49,0:09:23.10,On Top,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,CULTURAL & SPORTS GRAND FESTIVAL\NSPECIAL PARDON\NPARTICIPATE IN THE CEREMONY
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.47,0:09:25.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,and wholeheartedly toast the honor and\Nglory of Lady Satsuki and Lady Ragyo!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.10,0:09:26.58,On Top,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,CULTURAL & SPORTS GRAND FESTIVAL\NSPECIAL PARDON\NPARTICIPATE IN THE CEREMONY\NWHOLEHEARTEDLY TOAST
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.48,0:09:26.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Is that clear?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.11,0:09:30.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'd like to ask you two things.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.40,0:09:32.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.57,0:09:34.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Are the girls alive?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.57,0:09:35.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.12,0:09:41.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Question two!\NWill this ceremony be catered?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.66,0:09:44.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,O-Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.38,0:09:50.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Very well! On the honor of\Nthe Mankanshoku family,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.92,0:09:52.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,in order to remove our\Ndaughter's stigma,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.96,0:09:56.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,we shall clean our plates of this food,\Nleaving not one crumb uneaten!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.84,0:09:58.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Mark my words!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.10,0:10:04.08,On Top,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,CULTURAL & SPORTS GRAND FESTIVAL
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.60,0:10:04.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.56,0:10:08.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,A video feed from hidden cameras I had\Nset up inside Honnouji Academy.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.19,0:10:13.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If Ragyo Kiryuin is coming, too,\Nthis must be something big.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.15,0:10:14.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ragyo Kiryuin?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.20,0:10:18.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The leading figure of the\NKiryuin Conglomerate,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.03,0:10:21.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,and she's currently using\Nher position as REVOCS CEO
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.37,0:10:24.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,to sell clothing laced with Life Fibers\Nall around the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.54,0:10:28.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Good grief, she's blinding!\NShe's gaudier than Satsuki!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.54,0:10:30.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Like daughter skank,\Nlike mother skank.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.25,0:10:35.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,She's even more charismatic than Satsuki.\NShe's a formidable opponent.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.09,0:10:38.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.84,0:10:41.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,They're bringing in\NLife Fibers in bulk.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.51,0:10:42.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What are they up to?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.35,0:10:48.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, no... She plans to conduct the final\Nexperiment at Honnouji Academy!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.42,0:10:58.24,On Top,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,MILITARY REPURPOSING\NGOKU UNIFORMS\NEXPERIMENTATION CITY
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.27,0:10:52.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Honnouji Academy\Nis an experimentation city.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.73,0:10:57.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Goku Uniforms, created to study\Nhuman resistance to Life Fibers.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.32,0:11:01.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Repurposing them for military use and\Nconquering all of the country's academies.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.24,0:11:08.52,On Top,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,NATIONAL CONQUEST
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.28,0:11:05.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Then forcibly distributing Life Fiber-laced\Nuniforms to teenagers,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.37,0:11:08.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,those who have the\Nhighest resistance.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.79,0:11:10.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,After all that is complete,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.48,0:11:12.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,she offers up every\Nlast person gathered at Honnouji Academy
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.81,0:11:14.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,as human sacrifices\Nto the Life Fibers.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.98,0:11:16.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Human sacrifices?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.09,0:11:20.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. It must be her final experiment\Nto fully awaken the Life Fibers.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.76,0:11:24.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Gather a mass of people wearing\NLife Fiber-laced clothing in one spot
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.85,0:11:27.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,and then instantly convert\Nthem into Life Fibers.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.10,0:11:30.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That is the real purpose of the\NCultural & Sports Grand Festival.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.65,0:11:34.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, so you're saying \Nthat Mako's dad and mom
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.23,0:11:36.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,\Nare gonna be eaten by their clothes?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.65,0:11:38.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Put in simple terms,\NI suppose they will.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.65,0:11:41.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Eaten by their clothes...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.20,0:11:46.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Screw that! No way am I\Ngonna let that happen!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.00,0:11:47.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ryuko?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.41,0:11:53.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ragyo Kiryuin and Satsuki Kiryuin...\NI'm gonna take you both out!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.79,0:11:55.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Leap straight into\Nthe jaws of danger?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.88,0:12:00.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I'm gonna jump down its throat\Nand rip out its guts with my teeth!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.88,0:12:01.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ryuko!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.05,0:12:03.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.01,0:12:05.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't lose control again.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.76,0:12:08.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I won't make you shed\Nany more bitter tears.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.77,0:12:14.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,One way or another, I have to\Nsettle this fight with Satsuki.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.23,0:12:17.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Are you with me, Senketsu?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.19,0:12:18.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.57,0:12:20.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,This will be interesting.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.45,0:12:23.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh brother, I guess you\Nleave me no choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.49,0:12:27.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Let's hurry, then.\NWe don't have much time.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.04,0:12:34.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The Hyper Inner manufacturing facility\Nin Mozambique was attacked.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.17,0:12:36.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Militant extremists?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.96,0:12:42.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, ma'am. It would seem that even\Nantiestablishment organizations are awash
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.43,0:12:46.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,with rumors that wearing REVOCS special\Ninnerwear boosts physical capabilities.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.14,0:12:48.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That's fine.\NIt's exactly as planned.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.77,0:12:50.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We don't just\Nmake people buy them.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.60,0:12:53.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,There are some who are best tricked\Ninto taking them for themselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.90,0:12:55.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Regardless of how it came into\Ntheir possession, the end result
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.71,0:12:59.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,of them being worn by REVOCS clothing\Nwill remain unchanged.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.19,0:13:00.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What a beautiful world.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.78,0:13:02.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Not yet, we're only\Ngetting started.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.28,0:13:06.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Tomorrow, we step\Nonto a new stage.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.57,0:13:09.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The next step to the\Nawakening of COVERS.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.45,0:13:11.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Lady Satsuki is most impressive.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.12,0:13:13.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,She masterfully conquered\Nthe teen demographic,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.46,0:13:16.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,which has the highest resistance\Nto Life Fibers.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.75,0:13:19.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It was ingenious, negating their\Nresistance to Life Fibers
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.67,0:13:23.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,by getting them hooked on\Nthe power of Goku Uniforms.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.13,0:13:26.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But things are so dull\Nif they're too neat and tidy.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.05,0:13:27.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Grand Couturier...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.43,0:13:31.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, right. It was Matoi's daughter\Nthat you were more interested in.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.52,0:13:34.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. To think that she gathered up\Nthe pieces of her Kamui
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.77,0:13:37.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,and stitched them together\Nall by herself...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.40,0:13:41.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,There aren't many girls\Nwho can be quite that rude.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.08,0:13:45.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,"Fair is foul, and foul is fair," eh?\NHow very like you, Nui.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.32,0:13:46.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yep!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.28,0:13:49.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Still, that's mere empty rhetoric.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.73,0:13:51.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,\NThere is only one truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.12,0:13:56.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Only those things that earn Ragyo Kiryuin's\Napproval may be called beautiful.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.08,0:13:59.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The Cultural & Sports\NGrand Festival is tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.21,0:14:01.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I expect you to dress up\Nfor the occasion.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.01,0:14:07.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Enough to satisfy\Neven my sense of style.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.30,0:14:12.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Honestly, like mother,\Nlike daughter...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.27,0:14:14.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Tsumugu.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.35,0:14:16.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.64,0:14:19.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,A Tailor's Dagger\Nand Tailor's Glove.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.36,0:14:22.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,They're capable of\Ncutting Life Fibers.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.15,0:14:24.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You're at a disadvantage in
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.32,0:14:25.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,close combat with just \Nthose sewing machine guns.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.07,0:14:29.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Sever the Goku Uniform's Banshi\Nand my opponent goes stark naked, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.91,0:14:31.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Good. Very good.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.99,0:14:35.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Our targets are only Ragyo and Satsuki.\NIgnore everything else.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.83,0:14:39.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Well, it's not like there's anything else\Nwe can do with just three of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.29,0:14:41.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Keep Mako safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.34,0:14:41.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.24,0:14:45.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've asked our remaining\Nmembers to look after her here.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.88,0:14:48.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Don't ditch me here, Ryuko!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.22,0:14:50.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Mako...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.39,0:14:51.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,C'mon, let's go home!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.39,0:14:53.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Dummy, Honnouji Academy\Nisn't safe for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.81,0:14:55.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But it's my home!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.48,0:14:58.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've got souvenirs\Nto give to Dad and Mom!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.35,0:15:00.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Dammit, Mako!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.69,0:15:02.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If you're going, so am I!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.40,0:15:09.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh right, you don't listen once you've\Nmade up your mind, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.54,0:15:21.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Tomorrow is the long-awaited\NCultural & Sports Grand Festival!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.71,0:15:24.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I want you all to set to it with\Ndetermination in your hearts!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.67,0:15:25.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.96,0:15:27.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I can't hear you!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.84,0:15:29.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,YES, SIR!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.93,0:15:31.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Straighten out those lights a little!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.59,0:15:33.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Good, I want them\Nto wreathe the stage.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.64,0:15:35.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Tomorrow will be Honnouji Academy's climax!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.87,0:15:37.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,\NLet's make it more dramatic!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.60,0:15:38.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, right there!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.94,0:15:40.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Good, good!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.48,0:15:43.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Work fast, people!\NWe're in the home stretch!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.97,0:15:45.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}How are things coming\Ndown there, Iori?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.61,0:15:48.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's the day that Lady \NSatsuki has dreamed of.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.03,0:15:49.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,\NWe'll be ready come hell or high water.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.95,0:15:52.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Understood.\NI'll be done here soon, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.29,0:16:03.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It looks like the naked apes\Nhave taken the bait.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.71,0:16:06.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It was worth leaving those hidden\Ncameras where they were.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.71,0:16:09.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,This will fill in the final\Npiece of the puzzle.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.14,0:16:14.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Summon everyone to the\NStudent Council Chambers.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.85,0:16:19.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,All preparations to welcome\Nmy mother are now complete.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.19,0:16:22.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I appreciate all your hard work.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.40,0:16:22.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ma'am!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.40,0:16:26.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And so, let us toast the success of the\NCultural & Sports Grand Festival!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.68,0:16:54.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Attention, all students and families\Nof Honnouji Academy!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.97,0:16:58.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We have succeeded in conquering\Nof all the nation's academies!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.81,0:17:02.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,All of the fools who dared oppose our\NGoku Uniforms have been eliminated!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.77,0:17:04.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Today is a celebration\Nof those accomplishments!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.07,0:17:08.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Eat and drink your fill!\NPraise the Kiryuin name!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.28,0:17:13.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The Honnouji Academy Cultural & Sports\NGrand Festival begins now!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.04,0:17:26.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's begun, dear!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.79,0:17:29.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Who cares?! Just eat!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.92,0:17:32.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah! We'll stuff ourselves\Nand then skip out afterwards!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.01,0:17:36.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hold on, Mataro, Now that I have\Na good look at you, you're naked!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.84,0:17:39.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I sold off that stupid\Ndress uniform ages ago!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.39,0:17:41.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Damn, I wish I'd\Nthought of that!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.73,0:17:45.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And now, what you have all\Nbeen waiting for.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.52,0:17:48.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Let us offer a welcome\Nwith the utmost respect.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.44,0:17:54.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I present to you this academy's\Nfounder, Director Ragyo Kiryuin!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.31,0:18:31.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,As grand an entrance as one would\Nexpect from our director.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.40,0:18:35.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,A ruler must shine\Nlike the sun at all times.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.95,0:18:38.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It has been far too long, Mrs. Kiryuin.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.03,0:18:41.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, Nonon.\NHow is your father?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.33,0:18:42.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Fine, thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.87,0:18:47.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Are you still engaging in hacking\Nand stock manipulation?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.29,0:18:49.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I no longer indulge\Nin such things...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.21,0:18:51.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, you don't? A pity.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.76,0:18:57.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ladies and gentlemen,\NI put a question to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.93,0:18:59.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What is the world?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.55,0:19:02.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The world is clothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.18,0:19:06.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Life Fibers are the ruler\Nof this world.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.27,0:19:14.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I, Ragyo Kiryuin,\Nknow and carry out their will!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.69,0:19:17.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Honnouji Academy was created\Nfor just that purpose.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.86,0:19:20.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The weak will serve as the foundation\Nfor what is to come.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.74,0:19:23.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You should consider that\Nan honor.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.08,0:19:24.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What the heck is the Director\Ntalking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.41,0:19:27.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,She means that the day has come for
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.14,0:19:29.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the pigs in human clothing to \Nbe devoured by their clothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.21,0:19:33.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Now, let the celebration begin!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.58,0:19:47.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Dad! Mom!\NGuts, too?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.65,0:19:52.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What's that screaming?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.98,0:19:54.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Sounds like it's started.\NLet's hurry.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.36,0:19:59.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'll use the DTR to jump us\Nto the stage in one go.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.65,0:20:01.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, Tsumugu!\NRyuko!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.66,0:20:02.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You mean Dotonbori Robo?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.32,0:20:04.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,DTR!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.49,0:20:05.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's Dotonbori Robo, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.99,0:20:07.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,DTR!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.41,0:20:09.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,He hates that name.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.58,0:20:11.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You're worried about that\Nat a time like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.47,0:20:13.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What about me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.46,0:20:18.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I slipped off!\NThere's nowhere to grab on!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.30,0:20:20.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Go and hide!\NI'll give you snacks!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.68,0:20:24.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,DTR, going airborne!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.22,0:20:26.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Have fun storming the stadium!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.36,0:20:44.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Such wonderful silence...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.24,0:20:47.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The cacophony spewed forth \Nby the foolish creature
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.49,0:20:49.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,known as humanity fades away,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.37,0:20:52.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,and nothing but tranquil fibers\Nwill fill the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.87,0:20:56.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The experiment is a success,\NLady Ragyo!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.26,0:21:03.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm putting an end to this,\NSatsuki Kiryuin!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.01,0:21:04.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Turn everyone back to normal!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.80,0:21:09.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, so you are Ryuko Matoi?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.56,0:21:10.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You're—
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.39,0:21:13.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I see. And that is\NKamui Senketsu?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.65,0:21:17.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The fruits of Isshin Matoi's\Nlast, futile efforts.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.40,0:21:19.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I must say, I didn't expect it\Nto be so beautiful.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.28,0:21:22.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So you're Ragyo Kiryuin, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.57,0:21:25.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I swear, you Kiryuins love\Nto talk down to people!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.66,0:21:30.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I do. I am the one who knows\Neverything in this world.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.45,0:21:33.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I am the leader of the\NKiryuin Conglomerate, Rag—
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.09,0:21:41.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What are you playing at, Satsuki?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.55,0:21:43.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The time for speeches\Nis over, Director.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.90,0:22:10.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,As of this moment, Satsuki Kiryuin\Nand Honnouji Academy
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.08,0:22:12.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,are in rebellion against you!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.70,0:22:15.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What... the hell?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.46,0:22:18.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, so that's her game.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.29,0:22:21.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You're trying to take\Nthe throne from me?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.09,0:22:23.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,No, I'm not!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.88,0:22:28.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,People do not live\Nfor the sake of clothing!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.80,0:22:33.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I, Satsuki Kiryuin, am rising up\Nto overthrow Life Fibers!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.77,0:22:38.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Honnouji Academy is the fortress\NI created in order to defeat you!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.40,0:22:41.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Remember that, Ragyo Kiryuin!
